s=\"(max-width: 221px) 100vw, 221px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Paid Memberships Pro includes a <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/hook/pmpro_element_class/\">pmpro_element_class filter hook</a> that theme authors and plugin developers can use to dynamically add CSS selectors to frontend pages of Paid Memberships Pro. In this recipe, we swap all uses of the <code>pmpro_btn</code> selector with the Neve theme&#8217;s stylized <code>button button-primary</code> and other alternative selectors. </p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Code Recipe</h2>\n\n\n\nView the code on <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/JarrydLong/7d65b6a4f630df5ad7dec3413764c52f\">Gist</a>.\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Adding the Recipe to Your Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can add this recipe to your site by creating a custom plugin or using the Code Snippets plugin available for free in the WordPress repository.&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/create-a-plugin-for-pmpro-customizations\" target=\"_blank\">Read this companion article for step-by-step directions on either method</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"medium-2  columns\"><img class=\"avatar\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/images/Jarryd_Long.jpg\" alt=\"Jarryd Long\"/></div><div class=\"medium-10  columns\">\n<p class=\"lead\">This code recipe was written by our very own Jarryd Long.</p>\n<p></p></div></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/neve-theme-by-themeisle-paid-memberships-pro/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"Using the Hestia Theme by Themeisle with Paid Memberships Pro\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/hestia-theme-by-themeisle-paid-memberships-pro/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:90:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/hestia-theme-by-themeisle-paid-memberships-pro/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 09:22:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Recipes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"pmpro_element_class\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/?p=280969\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:481:\"The Hestia Theme by Themeisle is a popular free theme available in the WordPress.org Themes Directory. This guide will help you make Paid Memberships Pro look better with the Astra theme. Creating Compatibility for Hestia and PMPro Paid Memberships Pro includes a pmpro_element_class filter hook that theme authors and plugin developers can use to dynamically <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/hestia-theme-by-themeisle-paid-memberships-pro/\" rel=\"nofollow\">(more...)</a>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"Ansie Lima\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2062:\"<div class=\"lead\">\n<p>The <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/hestia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Hestia Theme by Themeisle</a> is a popular free theme available in the WordPress.org Themes Directory. This guide will help you make Paid Memberships Pro look better with the Astra theme.</p>\n\n\n\n</div><hr />\n\n\n\n<h2>Creating Compatibility for Hestia and PMPro</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image box-shadow\"><figure class=\"alignright size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Hestia-by-themeisle.png\" alt=\"Hestia by Themeisle\" class=\"wp-image-280970\" width=\"244\" height=\"185\"/></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Paid Memberships Pro includes a <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/hook/pmpro_element_class/\">pmpro_element_class filter hook</a> that theme authors and plugin developers can use to dynamically add CSS selectors to frontend pages of Paid Memberships Pro. In this recipe, we swap all uses of the <code>pmpro_btn</code> selector with the Hestia theme&#8217;s stylized <code>btn</code>selector. </p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Code Recipe</h2>\n\n\n\nView the code on <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/JarrydLong/98ef6b1f9cd76ad7980078b9933ca057\">Gist</a>.\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>Adding the Recipe to Your Website</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can add this recipe to your site by creating a custom plugin or using the Code Snippets plugin available for free in the WordPress repository.&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/create-a-plugin-for-pmpro-customizations\" target=\"_blank\">Read this companion article for step-by-step directions on either method</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n\n\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"medium-2  columns\"><img class=\"avatar\" src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/images/Jarryd_Long.jpg\" alt=\"Jarryd Long\"/></div><div class=\"medium-10  columns\">\n<p class=\"lead\">This code recipe was written by our very own Jarryd Long.</p>\n<p></p></div></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/hestia-theme-by-themeisle-paid-memberships-pro/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{