p>The <a href=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-ons/membership-maps/\">Membership Maps Add On for Paid Memberships Pro</a> is designed to geocode a member&#8217;s Billing Address information at membership checkout. If you are just installing this Add On, there are existing members in your site that have not yet had their address processed for display on the membership map.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>This recipe will run a batch process on 30 members at a time to properly geocode their information for display.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/membership-map-1-1024x515.jpg\" alt=\"membership map\" class=\"wp-image-280487\" srcset=\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/membership-map-1-1024x515.jpg 1024w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/membership-map-1-300x151.jpg 300w, https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/membership-map-1.jpg 1170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"pmpro_content_message\">This content is for members only. Visit the site and log in/register to read.</div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"Add a Membership Map to Your WordPress Website.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://www.paidmembershipspro.com/add-a-membership-map-to-your-wordpress-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\"